snippet.title: Steigar - Playthrough - Amiga
snippet.description:
No Longplay / Playthrough on YT of the Amiga version, so decided to make one. 
Short, subpar and quite easy shmup for the Amiga.
Endlessly looping after the few stages shown here.

Rating: 4/10
Difficulty: 2/10
BS rate: 3/10

Some of the problems I encounter might be caused by emulation, bad rom files or problems with the setup and might not actually be the games fault, but I have no way of testing this out, so please tell me if something feels off.
